        "subject": "LU-73 Client patch for RHEL6.",
        "message": "LU-73 Client patch for RHEL6.\n\n* This patch is needed in order to compile Lustre 2.x client on RHEL6\n2.6.32 kernel. Indeed, the 'shrink' field of 'struct shrinker' has\nchanged type in 2.6.32-71 (RHEL6 GA). (bz#22375)\n\n* Fix macro check for bdi interface. (bz# 23064)\n\nChange-Id: Ib6aebb5b3e28809cda0c1fb29e4ac80ed495f797\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
